t><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>III/IVspc</date>
<placeName cert="high">?</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>ταῖς κυρίαις μου <choice><corr>μητράσι</corr><sic>μητεραις</sic></choice> παρὰ Ἀθα-

    <lb n="2"/><expan><ex cert="high">να</ex></expan>σίου <choice><corr>χαίρειν</corr><sic>χαιρει</sic></choice>. πρὸ μὲν πάντων εὔ-

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>χομαι</corr><sic>ευχομε</sic></choice> τῶι <choice><corr>κ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">υ</supplied>ρίῳ</corr><sic>κριω</sic></choice> ἡμῶν θεῷ <choice><corr>ὁλοκληρεῖν</corr><sic>ολοκρηρειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ὑγιαίνειν</corr><sic>υενεν</sic></choice> σε. μαθὲ οὖν, κυρία μου μή-

    <lb n="5"/>τηρ, ὅτι <choice><corr cert="low">προσκυνῶ</corr><sic>προσσκ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υνω</unclear></sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τοὺς</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ποδὰς</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὑ</unclear>μῶν. 

    <lb n="6"/>μὴ <choice><corr>ἀγωνία</corr><sic>αγωνα</sic></choice> οὖν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">περὶ</unclear> μοῦ, <gap extent="6" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="7"/>εὐχαριστοῦμεν τῷ κυρίῳ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἡμῶν</supplied> 

    <lb n="8"/>θεῷ, ὅτι Ταὼς ἄρτι <choice><corr cert="low">συναπῆρε</corr><sic>συαπηρε</sic></choice>. ἀσπά-

    <lb n="9"/><choice><corr>ζομαι</corr><sic>ασπαζομε</sic></choice> τὸν κύριόν μου Παίσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>α καὶ τὴν 

    <lb n="10"/><choice><corr>κυρίαν</corr><sic>κυρια</sic></choice> μου <choice><corr>μητέρα</corr><sic>μητηρ<add place="supralinear">αν</add></sic></choice> καὶ τὴν ἀδελφήν 

    <lb n="11"/>μου Ὡριγενίαν <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κ</supplied>αὶ Θαεῖν καὶ Σοφίαν 

    <lb n="12"/>καὶ Δευκίλαν καὶ Εὐδαίμονα καὶ Ἡρα-

    <lb n="13"/>κλείδην καὶ Διονύσιον. <choice><corr>ἀσπάζομαι</corr><sic>ασποζομε</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="14"/>τὸν κύριόν μου ἀδελφὸν Πέκυλον 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ τὰ τέκνα αὐτοῦ. <choice><corr>ἀσπάζομαι</corr><sic>ασποζομε</sic></choice> Ζώσι-

    <lb n="16"/>μον καὶ Κάλοπον καὶ Ἡλλάλιβεν καὶ 

    <lb n="17"/>Μακεδόνιν καὶ <subst><add place="inline">Θατλῆν</add><del rend="corrected">θαθλην</del></subst> καὶ Πειπέ-

    <lb n="18"/>ριν καὶ Νίκην καὶ Ζωσίμην καὶ πάν-

    <lb n="19"/><subst><add place="inline">τας</add><del rend="corrected">παν<del rend="erasure">ν</del>τας</del></subst> τοὺς ὑμῶν κατ᾽ ὄνομα. 

    <lb n="20"/><choice><corr>ἐρρῶσθαί</corr><sic>ερωσθε</sic></choice> σε <choice><corr>εὔχομαι</corr><sic>ευχομε</sic></choice>, κυρία μου 

    <lb n="21"/>μήτηρ. προσαγορεύω <choice><corr>ὅλους</corr><sic>ορους</sic></choice> τοὺς 

    <lb n="22"/>ὑμῶν κατ᾽ ὄνομα. διευτύχει. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>τῇ κυρίᾳ μου <choice><corr>μητρὶ</corr><sic>μη<g type="x"/>τρι</sic></choice> παρ᾽ Ἀθανασίο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ</supplied> τῆς θυγατρός </ab></div></div><div n="meta.30581" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30581" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="201" type="textDate">III - IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.30581" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Berl. Zill.</title><biblScope type="numbers">12</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">30581</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0080</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">12</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0080;;12" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30581" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Youtie, Textual Criticism, Plate VII</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.30581" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Naldini, Cristianesimo 26</bibl></div><div n="meta.30581" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2006), S. 391</bibl><bibl type="translations">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2008), B12.2, Nr. 279</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.30581" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p>unbekannt</p></div></body></text></TEI.2>